msgid ""
"See :ref:`doc_kinematic_character_2d` for more details on using "
"``move_and_slide()``, including a demo project with detailed code."
msgstr ""
"有关使用 ``move_and_slide()`` 的更多详细信息，请参阅 :ref:"
